 />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zdVNVbT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzdVNVbT.jpg&h=e32702da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S0JPo5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS0JPo5d.jpg&h=bbac4125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ACwdQLe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FACwdQLe.jpg&h=cfeb6141&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e1gQSYz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe1gQSYz.jpg&h=d397a16b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QiGA35f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQiGA35f.jpg&h=c407c34f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T17:34:46.000Z","msg":"記得! 記得寫信, 因為收到真係會好warm , 同埋可以耐唔耐睇番.<br />\n雖然我果時收到ex既一封信, 係叫我以後唔好再寫信比佢, 過得好好, 大家斷絕來往 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好過咩都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識佢地既朋友探佢地既時候記得入埋相, 耐唔耐可以睇番差好遠.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:14:25.000Z","msg":"辛苦你啦手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd150011963583eb93f7dab4c01a262f96b72f7","tid":1776731,"uid":161208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"546942b7ab06776b6932b4fde45f738c99ac5ef4","tid":1776731,"uid":11463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:01:06.000Z","msg":"想問唔食煙可唔可以扮有食入煙 keep住黎買野 咁做有冇咩壞處，畀人識穿會點，同埋讀書有冇話要最少要坐幾耐先有得報讀(3月上庭，想知多啲)唔該巴打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:17:20.000Z","msg":"辛苦你手足，你要加油"},{"pid":"3c700111f5faacf90e2f71b13a9d42444df43f43","tid":1776731,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430438ce48f76775d652237616d44632b2587394","tid":1776731,"uid":157654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:33:38.000Z","msg":"入面有無冷氣？"},{"pid":"109c219e6e6b176f3bc42d26bb48011e637d142f","tid":1776731,"uid":339090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"546942b7ab06776b6932b4fde45f738c99ac5ef4","tid":1776731,"uid":11463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:01:06.000Z","msg":"想問唔食煙可唔可以扮有食入煙 keep住黎買野 咁做有冇咩壞處，畀人識穿會點，同埋讀書有冇話要最少要坐幾耐先有得報讀(3月上庭，想知多啲)唔該巴打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:48:06.000Z","msg":"夠21?  判完刑會去荔枝角等過介<br />\n判完刑之後就冇得入煙入野食架喇 , 你要自己用入面既糧買.<br />\n唔駛扮, 冇人會理你<br />\n佢會問你食唔食,  食既就去有煙既監房 <br />\n唔食既就去無煙監房.(東頭/白沙)  (個人覺得無煙係好d )<br />\n不過有煙既就多d野玩 (詳情可以睇番上一個post)<br />\n未夠21 就一定無煙架喇, 唔駛諗<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csd.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/qa/qa.html#q26\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Finfo%2Fqa%2Fqa.html%23q26&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=ad39cf9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.csd.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/qa/qa.html#q26</a><br />\n可以睇一睇呢條link , 第38條<br />\n刑期幾耐先有得讀我就唔係好清楚, 我係成人監房<br />\n原post好似有人講過係唔知1年定2年<br />\n頂住呀手足 , 希望你冇事, 直接係出面繼續讀."},{"pid":"ca2feb97d6b1a8f822860977e3bda6d36ebf94a7","tid":1776731,"uid":339090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"430438ce48f76775d652237616d44632b2587394","tid":1776731,"uid":157654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:33:38.000Z","msg":"入